<main>
      <div class="container">
          <h3 class="myMainHeader py-3 text-center"><b>External Events</b></h3>
          
              <p class="pd-2">
                  <center>External events are a great opportunity for students who arenâ€™t familiar with our organization and want to <b>get to know us better!</b>
                  Through your participation in such event, be sure that you will gain valuable skills, have fun and get to know many like-minded people.
                  <br>So what are you waiting for? Apply in as many actions as you wish from the list below:</center><br>
              </p>

              <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between">
                {{#if events}}
                  {{#each events}}
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                      <div class="card-body">
                        <center>
                          <h5 class="card-title"><b>{{name}}</b></h5>
                          <h6>{{place}}, {{start_date}}</h6>
                          <p class="card-text"><a href="#" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#myModal{{id}}" class="text-to-click"><b>see more....</b></a></p>
                          <a href="/externalEvents/apply/{{id}}" class="btn btn-dark mb-3">apply</a>                        
                        </center>
                      </div>
                    </div>    
                    <div class="modal events-modals" id="myModal{{id}}" style="display: none;">
                      <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                        <div class="modal-content">
                          <div class="modal-header">
                            <h5 class="modal-title">{{name}}</h5>
                          </div>
                          <div class="modal-body">
                            <p>{{description}}</p>
                          </div>
                          <div class="modal-footer">
                            
                            <a href="/externalEvents/apply/{{id}}" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#myEventApplyModal{{id}}" class="btn btn-dark mb-3" id="myApplyButton">apply</a>                        
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-dark" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Back</button>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  {{/each}}
                {{/if}}
                {{#else}}
                  <h5>Sadly there are no upcoming events. Stay tuned though, because there will be many of them soon!</h5>
                {{/else}}     
              </div>
              
              <div id="myEventApplyModal{{id}}" class="modal" style="display: none;">
                  <div id="myEventApplyModalContent" class="modal-content py-2 px-4">
                    <span class="close">&times;</span>
                      <form action="/externalEvents/apply/{{id}}" method="POST">
                        <h3 class="mb-2">Apply</h3>
                          <div class="row py-4">
                              <div class="col">
                                <label for="InputName"><b>Name</b></label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="ApplicationName1" placeholder="Enter your Name" required>
                              </div>
                              <div class="col">
                                <label for="InputSurname"><b>Surname</b></label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="ApplicationSurname1" placeholder="Enter your Surname" required>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row pb-4">
                              <div class="col">
                                <label for="InputEmail"><b>Email address</b></label>
                                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="ApplicationEmail1" placeholder="Enter email" required>
                              </div>
                              <div class="col">
                                <label for="InputPhoneNumber"><b>Phone Number</b></label>
                                <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="ApplicationPhoneNumber2" placeholder="Enter phone number" required>
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark mb-5 mt-3">Apply</button>
                      </form>
                  </div>
                </div>

      </div>
  </main>
